headline: US Stock Market Today: S&P 500 Futures Edge Higher As Inflation Expectations Cool
summary: The Morning Bull - US Market Morning Update Tuesday, Feb, 10 2026 US stock futures are slightly higher this morning, with E-mini S&P 500 contracts up about 0.05% and Dow futures also edging into positive territory, as investors focus on falling bond yields and cooling inflation expectations. The US 10 year Treasury yield has dipped below 4.2%, which can ease borrowing costs for households and companies.
